<p class="ayah 28-16" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"My Lord!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ظَلَمْتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[I] have wronged</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْسِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">my soul,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱغْفِرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so forgive</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[for] me."</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَغَفَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then He forgave</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥٓ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[for] him.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed He,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He (is)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْغَفُورُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Oft-Forgiving,</span></span><span class="word stati