<p class="ayah 28-20" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَجَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And came</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَجُلٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a man</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَقْصَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) farthest end</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَدِينَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the city</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسْعَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">running.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰمُوسَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"O Musa!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَلَأَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the chiefs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَأْتَمِرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">are taking counsel</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِيَقْتُلُوكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to kill you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱخْرُجْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so leave;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">indeed, I am</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّـٰصِحِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sincere advisors."</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/28:20" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="3272"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>20<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
