<p class="ayah 28-64" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And it will be said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱدْعُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Call</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شُرَكَآءَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your partners."</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَدَعَوْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they will call them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسْتَجِيبُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they will respond</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَرَأَوُاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they will see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَذَابَ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the punishment.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">If only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[that] they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir